msgctxt "16176"
msgid "Zhao"
msgstr "Zhao"

msgctxt "16180"
msgid "Tanimura"
msgstr "Tanimura"

msgctxt "16184"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "16188"
msgid "Hisai"
msgstr "Hisai"

msgctxt "16192"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "16196"
msgid "Talk_Gakkari"
msgstr "Talk_Gakkari"

msgctxt "16200"
msgid "Talk_Ase"
msgstr "Talk_Ase"

msgctxt "16204"
msgid "Talk_NoBig"
msgstr "Talk_NoBig"

msgctxt "88_Zhao"
msgid "Oh, Ma-chan, you're back. How'd the thing go?"
msgstr "Oh, Ma-chan, you're back. How'd the thing go?"

msgctxt "100_Tanimura"
msgid "Well, I found the case report for the hit."
msgstr "Well, I found the case report for the hit."

msgctxt "112_Zhao"
msgid "You did!? What did it say!?"
msgstr "You did!? What did it say!?"

msgctxt "124_Tanimura"
msgid "A lot of stuff I already knew, plus one new piece of info."
msgstr "A lot of stuff I already knew, plus one new piece of info."

msgctxt "136_Zhao"
msgid "Oh?"
msgstr "Oh..."

msgctxt "148_Tanimura"
msgid "Sugiuchi was investigating that case... along with my dad."
msgstr "Sugiuchi was investigating that case... along with my dad."

msgctxt "160_Zhao"
msgid "Sugiuchi? The same one that's always giving you hell back at the station?"
msgstr "Sugiuchi? The same one that's always giving you hell back at the station?"

msgctxt "172_Tanimura"
msgid "Mhm. I've talked to him more times than I care to remember, but he never once mentioned being on a case with my dad."
msgstr "Mhm. I've talked to him more times than I care to remember, but he never once mentioned being on a case with my dad."

msgctxt "184_Tanimura"
msgid "And that's despite him knowing how bad I want the truth."
msgstr "And that's despite him knowing how bad I want the truth."

msgctxt "196_Zhao"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "208_Tanimura"
msgid "That's not the worst of it, either. I'm starting to believe someone on the force did my father in."
msgstr "That's not the worst of it, either. I'm starting to believe someone on the force did my father in."

msgctxt "220_Tanimura"
msgid "Katsuragi said as much when we met yesterday."
msgstr "Katsuragi said as much when we met yesterday."

msgctxt "232_Zhao"
msgid "Another officer... Things just keep getting better, huh?"
msgstr "Another officer... Things just keep getting better, huh?"

msgctxt "244_Tanimura"
msgid "Seriously..."
msgstr "Seriously..."

msgctxt "256_Zhao"
msgid "Why don't you call it a day, Ma-chan? Even you need to rest at some point."
msgstr "Why don't you call it a day, Ma-chan? Even you need to rest at some point."

msgctxt "268_Tanimura"
msgid "...You're right. I think I'll knock out for a while."
msgstr "...You're right. I think I'll knock out for a while."

msgctxt "280_Zhao"
msgid "You do that."
msgstr "Hazlo."

msgctxt "292_Zhao"
msgid "Hey, Mei Hua! Get Ma-chan's futon ready!"
msgstr "Hey, Mei Hua! Get Ma-chan's futon ready!"

msgctxt "340_Hisai"
msgid "Either way, Tanimura-kun, that stunt you pulled had me worried half to death!"
msgstr "Either way, Tanimura-kun, that stunt you pulled had me worried half to death!"

msgctxt "352_Hisai"
msgid "I got a call from Sugiuchi-kun in Homicide telling me you were trying to contact the Ueno Seiwa."
msgstr "I got a call from Sugiuchi-kun in Homicide telling me you were trying to contact the Ueno Seiwa."

msgctxt "364_Hisai"
msgid "So I took it upon myself to search for you before you wound up in danger... Which ended up happening anyway!"
msgstr "So I took it upon myself to search for you before you wound up in danger... Which ended up happening anyway!"

msgctxt "376_Tanimura"
msgid "Ahh, so that's why you're here."
msgstr "Ahh, so that's why you're here."

msgctxt "388_Hisai"
msgid "Tanimura-kun. You must have some inclination as to how dangerous the Ueno Seiwa Clan is right now. Are you even aware of the gravity of this situation?"
msgstr "Tanimura-kun. You must have some inclination as to how dangerous the Ueno Seiwa Clan is right now. Are you even aware of the gravity of this situation?"

msgctxt "400_Tanimura"
msgid "Eh, more or less."
msgstr "Eh, more or less."

msgctxt "412_Hisai"
msgid "*sigh*"
msgstr "*suspiro*"

msgctxt "424_Zhao"
msgid "Well, at least this Katsuragi seems to know something about your father's killer."
msgstr "Well, at least this Katsuragi seems to know something about your father's killer."

msgctxt "436_Zhao"
msgid "Sounds like progress to me."
msgstr "Sounds like progress to me."

msgctxt "448_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, I guess that's one way to look at it..."
msgstr "Yeah, I guess that's one way to look at it..."

msgctxt "460_Zhao"
msgid "Then why the long face? You finally have a promising lead."
msgstr "Then why the long face? You finally have a promising lead."

msgctxt "472_Tanimura"
msgid "Something that Katsuragi said has been bugging me."
msgstr "Something that Katsuragi said has been bugging me."

msgctxt "484_Zhao"
msgid "And what was that?"
msgstr "And what was that?"

msgctxt "496_Tanimura"
msgid "The police covered up the truth about the massacre in 1985."
msgstr "The police covered up the truth about the massacre in 1985."

msgctxt "508_Tanimura"
msgid "They knew the real killer was Katsuragi, but they pinned it all on Saejima."
msgstr "They knew the real killer was Katsuragi, but they pinned it all on Saejima."

msgctxt "520_Zhao"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Uh, ¿y eso?"

msgctxt "532_Hisai"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

msgctxt "544_Tanimura"
msgid "None of this rings a bell, Chief?"
msgstr "None of this rings a bell, Chief?"

msgctxt "556_Hisai"
msgid "No. I'm not in Homicide, and back then I was as low on the totem pole as it gets."
msgstr "No. I'm not in Homicide, and back then I was as low on the totem pole as it gets."

msgctxt "568_Tanimura"
msgid "Fair enough."
msgstr "Así es."

msgctxt "580_Zhao"
msgid "So were the police trying to protect Katsuragi? If so, why?"
msgstr "So were the police trying to protect Katsuragi? If so, why?"

msgctxt "592_Tanimura"
msgid "Who knows? But they obviously couldn't let a scandal like that go public."
msgstr "Who knows? But they obviously couldn't let a scandal like that go public."

msgctxt "604_Zhao"
msgid "Hrm..."
msgstr "Hrm..."

msgctxt "628_Hisai"
msgid "...I just thought of something."
msgstr "...I just thought of something."

msgctxt "640_Tanimura"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "¿Mm?"

msgctxt "652_Hisai"
msgid "Maybe we could dig something up at headquarters."
msgstr "Maybe we could dig something up at headquarters."

msgctxt "664_Tanimura"
msgid "Oh yeah? How?"
msgstr "Oh yeah? How?"

msgctxt "676_Hisai"
msgid "Archive Room 13 on basement level 3...\\r\n"\n"The so-called Forbidden Room."
msgstr "Archive Room 13 on basement level 3...\\r\n"\n"The so-called Forbidden Room."

msgctxt "688_Zhao"
msgid "Forbidden Room!?"
msgstr "Forbidden Room!?"

msgctxt "700_Hisai"
msgid "That's right. Also known as the \"Scandal Graveyard.\""
msgstr "That's right. Also known as the \"Scandal Graveyard.\""

msgctxt "712_Hisai"
msgid "All records of police misconduct over the years supposedly end up there."
msgstr "All records of police misconduct over the years supposedly end up there."

msgctxt "724_Hisai"
msgid "Or so the rumor goes."
msgstr "Or so the rumor goes."

msgctxt "736_Tanimura"
msgid "Interesting. Then we just might find something useful."
msgstr "Interesting. Then we just might find something useful."

msgctxt "748_Hisai"
msgid "Yes. Or, well, it could all simply be a rumor."
msgstr "Yes. Or, well, it could all simply be a rumor."

msgctxt "760_Tanimura"
msgid "Still, worth a shot. In fact... I'm all over it."
msgstr "Still, worth a shot. In fact... I'm all over it."

msgctxt "772_Hisai"
msgid "Now hold your horses, Tanimura-kun! Think about it. Archive 13 is smack-dab in the middle of headquarters!"
msgstr "Now hold your horses, Tanimura-kun! Think about it. Archive 13 is smack-dab in the middle of headquarters!"

msgctxt "784_Hisai"
msgid "A rookie like you can't just go strolling in there without permission."
msgstr "A rookie like you can't just go strolling in there without permission."

msgctxt "796_Tanimura"
msgid "I never planned on asking. I mean, we're dealing with someone who can cover up mass murder."
msgstr "I never planned on asking. I mean, we're dealing with someone who can cover up mass murder."

msgctxt "808_Tanimura"
msgid "I doubt they'd be keen on giving me access to the evidence."
msgstr "I doubt they'd be keen on giving me access to the evidence."

msgctxt "820_Zhao"
msgid "You serious about this, Ma-chan...?"
msgstr "You serious about this, Ma-chan...?"

msgctxt "832_Hisai"
msgid "Tanimura-kun, I... No, nothing."
msgstr "Tanimura-kun, I... No, nothing."

msgctxt "844_Tanimura"
msgid "So. We all ready to go?"
msgstr "So. We all ready to go?"

msgctxt "856_Hisai"
msgid "Huh? Wait... \"We\" as in you and me?"
msgstr "Huh? Wait... \"We\" as in you and me?"

msgctxt "868_Tanimura"
msgid "Of course! Us Community Safety boys gotta stick together, right? Besides, I've only been to HQ maybe once or twice."
msgstr "Of course! Us Community Safety boys gotta stick together, right? Besides, I've only been to HQ maybe once or twice."

msgctxt "880_Tanimura"
msgid "I probably couldn't find this archive even if I tried."
msgstr "I probably couldn't find this archive even if I tried."

msgctxt "892_Tanimura"
msgid "But you know right where it is, don't you, Chief?"
msgstr "But you know right where it is, don't you, Chief?"

msgctxt "904_Hisai"
msgid "What? No, I... Well, I mean, yes, but be that as it may..."
msgstr "What? No, I... Well, I mean, yes, but be that as it may..."

msgctxt "916_Tanimura"
msgid "Great! Then I'll be counting on you!"
msgstr "Great! Then I'll be counting on you!"

msgctxt "940_Zhao"
msgid "What!? You mean someone else killed those 18 men?"
msgstr "¿¡Qué!? ¿Dices que alguien más mató a esos 18 hombres?"

msgctxt "952_Tanimura"
msgid "Right. The Ueno Seiwa officers were taken out by one of their own: Katsuragi."
msgstr "Right. The Ueno Seiwa officers were taken out by one of their own: Katsuragi."

msgctxt "964_Zhao"
msgid "Then Yasuko Saejima's brother is innocent?"
msgstr "Then Yasuko Saejima's brother is innocent?"

msgctxt "976_Tanimura"
msgid "Well, he did carry out the attack, so he's far from innocent."
msgstr "Well, he did carry out the attack, so he's far from innocent."

msgctxt "988_Tanimura"
msgid "But there's a big difference in sentencing for murder and attempted murder."
msgstr "But there's a big difference in sentencing for murder and attempted murder."

msgctxt "1000_Zhao"
msgid "Hrm..."
msgstr "Hrm..."

msgctxt "1012_Hisai"
msgid "Was this Katsuragi also responsible for killing your father?"
msgstr "Was this Katsuragi also responsible for killing your father?"

msgctxt "1024_Tanimura"
msgid "I couldn't get an answer out of him."
msgstr "I couldn't get an answer out of him."

msgctxt "1036_Hisai"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

